It's a nightmare! We have to get back outside Amicia! I know, keep moving!

168
00:13:33,637 --> 00:13:37,919
Now another quick video to hear how we showcase the rats thanks to Music Stingers. The cello is

169
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:44,342
once again featured heavily. When the player was hearing this cello, he knew directly there would

170
00:13:44,342 --> 00:13:44,922
be rats around.

171
00:13:48,473 --> 00:13:50,053
In the light! In the light! Quick!

172
00:13:50,053 --> 00:13:52,534
I don't see a torch.

